items.text: **Braden Webb** (raised in [[LINK|lang_en|Owasso,_Oklahoma|Owasso, Oklahoma]]) is an [[LINK|lang_en|Americans|American]] [[LINK|lang_en|Student|student]] and [[LINK|lang_en|sport|athlete]]. He plays for [[LINK|lang_en|South_Carolina_Gamecocks|South Carolina Gamecocks]] and is affiliated with the [[LINK|lang_en|National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association|National Collegiate Athletic Association]].
